<div data-label="Row" id="r-1597418193937" class="gf_row" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1597418193937"><div class="gf_col-lg-12 gf_column" id="c-1597418193873" data-id="1597418193873"><div data-label="Heading" id="e-1597418210323" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="1" data-id="1597418210323"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h1>Head of Influencer Marketing DACH (f/m/d)</h1></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" id="e-1597418201952" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1597418201952"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left" data-gemlang="en"><p></p><div class="page" title="Page 1"><div class="section"><div class="layoutArea"><div class="column"><p><span style="font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'ArialMT'">At </span><span style="font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Gautami'">​</span><span style="font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Arial'; font-weight: 700">gitti </span><span style="font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Gautami'">​</span><span style="font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'ArialMT'">we revolutionize the beauty industry with new, innovative, vegan beauty products.We reunite two concepts that the traditional beauty industry seems to have opposed in the last years: <b>beauty from inside and outside</b>. What does this mean for us? We strive for a dual power of beauty and mindfulness: we make beauty sustainable by caring for ourselves and our planet. We want to wake this industry up and offer better alternatives, because you and our planet deserve better. We know we can't do this alone. Changing a mindset requires true heroes who consciously live beauty every day and lead the way.</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'ArialMT'">gitti is a dynamic start-up based in Berlin with a highly passionate team and an outstanding company culture. We are now looking for a </span><span style="font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Gautami'">​</span><span style="font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Arial'; font-weight: 700">Head of Influencer Marketing DACH (m/f/x).</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'Arial'; font-weight: 700"><br></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'ArialMT'"><b>Your tasks</b></span></p><p><span style="font-family: ArialMT; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: 0px;">● &nbsp;develop, implement, execute, evaluate and optimate influencer marketing strategies&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ArialMT; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: 0px;">and campaigns together with your team</span></p><p><span style="font-family: ArialMT; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: 0px;">● &nbsp;identify new influencers and brand ambassadors</span></p><p><span style="font-family: ArialMT; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: 0px;">● manage and maintain influencer- and agency relationships</span></p><p><span style="font-family: ArialMT; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: 0px;">● &nbsp;own the budget for the DACH influencer department</span></p><p><span style="font-family: ArialMT; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: 0px;">● &nbsp;monitor trends and competitors; prepare weekly Marketing reports</span></p><p><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: ArialMT;">● &nbsp;</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: ArialMT;">manage your team (5-7 people) with structure, guidance and mentorship</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'ArialMT'"><br></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'ArialMT'"><b>Your profile</b></span></p><p><span style="font-family: ArialMT; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: 0px;">● &nbsp;ideally you have a background as a Head of Influencer Marketing in e-commerce or&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ArialMT; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: 0px;">sales; ideally in another D2C start-up</span></p><p><span style="font-family: ArialMT; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: 0px;">● &nbsp;you have a data-driven mindset, excellent analytical skills as well as strong&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ArialMT; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: 0px;">negotiating- and excel power</span></p><p><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: ArialMT;">●&nbsp; you&nbsp;</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: ArialMT;">have the ability to balance metrics-focused thinking with the strong creative mind needed to develop breakthrough authentic and engaging campaigns</span></p><p><span style="font-family: ArialMT; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: 0px;">● &nbsp;you have a growth mindset and can-do-mentality</span></p><p><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: ArialMT;">● &nbsp;</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: ArialMT;">you are fluent in both english &amp; german: written &amp; verbal</span></p><p><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: ArialMT;">● &nbsp;</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: ArialMT;">you have previously led a team and have solid experience managing people</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'ArialMT'"><br></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: 'ArialMT'"><b>Your benefits</b></span></p><p><span style="font-family: ArialMT; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: 0px;">● &nbsp;join an international, fast growing start-up with flat hierarchies, short decision-making&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ArialMT; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: 0px;">path and room to actively shape the company</span></p><p><span style="font-family: ArialMT; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: 0px;">● &nbsp;be part of an ambitious and empowering team that strongly focuses on sustainability</span></p><p><span style="font-family: ArialMT; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: 0px;">● &nbsp;a culture of trust and empowerment in a positive and inspiring work atmosphere</span></p><p><span style="font-family: ArialMT; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: 0px;">● &nbsp;receive market standard salary and additional perks such as public transportation</span></p><p><span style="font-family: ArialMT; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: 0px;">● &nbsp;enjoy our spacious and central Berlin office, the flexibility to integrate remote working&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ArialMT; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: 0px;">hours and an outstanding team spirit &amp; company culture.</span></p><p><span style="font-family: ArialMT; font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: 0px;">Sounds like a fit? Please send your CV, salary expectations and your earliest possible starting date to <b>jobs@gitti.de</b>. The beauty industry is changing fast, support us to re-inventit. We cannot wait to meet you!</span></p><ul style="list-style-type: none"><li><p><span style="font-size: 9.000000pt; font-family: 'Arial'; font-style: italic">“variety is the spice of life” — and a celebrated component of our culture. At gitti, we strive to create an inclusive environment that empowers our employees. We believe that our products benefit from our diverse backgrounds and experiences and are proud to be an equal opportunity employer: all qualified applicants are considered for positions regardless of race, ethnic origin, gender, age, religion or belief, marital status, gender identification,sexual orientation, or disability"</span></p></li></ul></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><!--gfsplit-->
